text = "Blackboard

Blackboard is the component that provides a service to store and retrieve data to be used to share state between scenes (CRUD). 

There are two main components:

- The Server side that manage all the data. It initializes the scenes (Repositories) with the initial data.
- The Client side that acts like a repository to abstract the way the data is managed. Repositories can store data into the Server to be shared among other subscenes.

In the example, three key/values are stored into the Blackboard and consumed by a SubScene."
